---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Testimonials for Bookkeepers — SocialProof" description="Collect client testimonials on autopilot. SocialProof helps bookkeepers and accounting professionals turn happy clients into referrals with a single shareable link." canonical="https://socialproof.dev/for/bookkeepers">
<style>
    .hero { padding: 80px 24px 56px; text-align: center; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: 2.8rem; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.15; color: #111; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .hero p { font-size: 1.25rem; color: #555; margin-bottom: 36px; }
    .hero .cta-group { display: flex; gap: 14px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .why-section { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 24px; }
    .why-section h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 16px; text-align: center; }
    .why-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap: 28px; margin-top: 40px; }
    .why-card { background: #f9f9f9; border-radius: 12px; padding: 28px; }
    .why-card h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .why-card p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; }
    .steps-section { background: #f5f3ff; padding: 60px 24px; }
    .steps-inner { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; }
    .steps-inner h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 40px; }
    .steps-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; text-align: left; }
    .step { display: flex; gap: 18px; align-items: flex-start; }
    .step-num { background: #6c47ff; color: #fff; border-radius: 50%; width: 36px; height: 36px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .step-content h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .step-content p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; }
    .vs-section { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 24px; }
    .vs-section h2 { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 24px; text-align: center; }
    .vs-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    .vs-table th { text-align: left; padding: 12px 16px; background: #f9f9f9; color: #555; font-weight: 600; }
    .vs-table td { padding: 12px 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; color: #333; }
    .vs-table td.proof { color: #16a34a; font-weight: 600; }
    .vs-table td.them { color: #dc2626; }
    .quote-section { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 60px 24px; text-align: center; }
    .quote-section blockquote { font-size: 1.3rem; font-style: italic; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 16px; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 16px; }
    .quote-section cite { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #888; }
    .cta-section { background: #111; color: #fff; padding: 60px 24px; text-align: center; }
    .cta-section h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .cta-section p { font-size: 1.1rem; color: #aaa; margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .btn-primary { background: #6c47ff; color: #fff; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; }
    .btn-secondary { background: transparent; color: #111; border: 1.5px solid #ccc; padding: 13px 28px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; }
    .btn-white { background: #fff; color: #111; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; }
    nav { border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; padding: 16px 24px; }
    .nav-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
    .logo { font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.2rem; color: #111; text-decoration: none; }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 24px; align-items: center; }
    .nav-links a { color: #555; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.95rem; }
</style>

<nav>
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <a href="/" class="logo">SocialProof</a>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="/pricing">Pricing</a>
      <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn-primary" style="padding:10px 20px;font-size:0.9rem;">Start Free</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<section class="hero">
  <h1>Your best clients say great things.<br />Let the world hear them.</h1>
  <p>SocialProof helps bookkeepers and accounting professionals collect client testimonials with one shareable link — no tech skills required.</p>
  <div class="cta-group">
    <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn-primary">Start Free — No Credit Card</a>
    <a href="/demo" class="btn-secondary">See How It Works</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="why-section">
  <h2>Why bookkeepers need testimonials</h2>
  <p style="text-align:center;color:#555;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto 20px;">When someone's looking for a bookkeeper, trust is everything. They're handing you their financial records. A few genuine client testimonials close more deals than any ad.</p>
  <div class="why-grid">
    <div class="why-card">
      <h3>📣 Referrals don't scale. Testimonials do.</h3>
      <p>Word of mouth is your #1 source of new clients — but testimonials let you show that social proof to strangers, 24/7, on your website.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-card">
      <h3>🔍 Prospects Google you first</h3>
      <p>Before a potential client calls, they check your site. A testimonial widget on your homepage does the selling for you before you pick up the phone.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-card">
      <h3>💼 Differentiate from big firms</h3>
      <p>You have something national bookkeeping chains can't offer: real, personal relationships. Testimonials from real local clients prove that in a way no logo can.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-card">
      <h3>⏱ Stop chasing reviews</h3>
      <p>Forget the awkward "could you leave me a Google review?" moment. SocialProof sends a professional one-click link — clients respond in under a minute.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="steps-section">
  <div class="steps-inner">
    <h2>Set up in 10 minutes. Start collecting tomorrow.</h2>
    <div class="steps-list">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">1</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Create your free account</h3>
          <p>Sign up in 30 seconds — no credit card, no IT department. Free forever for 1 active widget.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">2</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Copy your testimonial link</h3>
          <p>Share it via email or text after you close a client's books each month. Clients click the link and leave a testimonial — no account needed on their end.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">3</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Paste a widget on your site</h3>
          <p>One line of code. Your testimonials display beautifully on your website, updating automatically as new ones come in.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="vs-section">
  <h2>SocialProof vs. sending people to Google</h2>
  <table class="vs-table">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Feature</th>
        <th>SocialProof</th>
        <th>Google Reviews</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>Clients need a Google account?</td>
        <td class="proof">No</td>
        <td class="them">Yes</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>You control how it looks on your site</td>
        <td class="proof">Yes — fully customizable widget</td>
        <td class="them">No</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Works with your website (any platform)</td>
        <td class="proof">Yes — one embed code</td>
        <td class="them">Limited</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Testimonials can't be taken down by a competitor</td>
        <td class="proof">Yes</td>
        <td class="them">No</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Free to start</td>
        <td class="proof">Yes — free forever for 1 widget</td>
        <td class="them">Free but you can't display on your site</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<section class="quote-section">
  <blockquote>"I emailed my top 10 clients the link on a Monday. By Wednesday I had 8 new testimonials on my website. My next inquiry mentioned them in our first call."</blockquote>
  <cite>— Sarah T., independent bookkeeper</cite>
</section>

<section class="cta-section">
  <h2>Start collecting testimonials today</h2>
  <p>Free forever for 1 active widget. No credit card. No tech skills needed.</p>
  <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn-white">Get Started Free →</a>
</section>
</Base>
